dc_title_s: North Atlantic Ocean, Greenland (Denmark)--west coast, Qaqortoq (Julianehåb) and approaches including Skovfjord (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From Danish charts to 1991." Shipping list no.: 2000-2005-S. "Copyright 1999 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." Place names in Danish with glossary in English. Inset: Qaqortoq (Julianehåb). Scale 1:4,000. "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Map No. 38588. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
